actual.value:
2015:34 CPS
The coverage of multilingual ECE increased from 22 to 34 CPS in five provinces. This marked the first expansion of the programme since its inception in 2011.

title.narrative: Government Early Childhood Care and Development National Action Plan (ECCD NAP) is operationalized

actual.value:
2015:ECCD NAP Results Framework officially approved
The Framework sets out the key indicators and annual targets. The M&E Framework facilitates systematic review of implementation based on the existing planning and budgeting systems at national and subnational levels.
